snippet.title: 'Chit Funds Prospered Under Politicians': PM Slams Mamata Banerjee On Note Ban

localized.description:
Prime Minister Narendra Modi today took a swipe at West Bengal Chief Minister Mamata Banjeree who has slammed his government's move to ban Rs 500 and 1000 notes. Speaking at a rally in Agra, the PM, without naming Ms Banerjee, said, "Chit funds prospered under politicians. Now they question me."
